-- Ukraine’s Grain Crop Totals 58.18 Million Tons, Researcher Says
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2011-12-21T15:53:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-21/ukraine-s-grain-crop-totals-58-18-million-tons-researcher-says.html
Ukraine’s grain harvest totaled
58.18 million metric tons as of yesterday, UkrAgroConsult said.  Farmers reaped grain from 99.8 percent of planted areas,
the researcher said in an e-mailed statement today without
giving a year-ago comparison. Average grain yields rose to 3.8
tons a hectare (2.47 acres) from 2.85 tons a hectare last year,
it said. The corn harvest was 22.6 million tons, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
